original_title: Strassman Live Vol. 4: Ted E's Farewell
overview: The much adored Ted E. Bare has announced his showbiz retirement and, in this side-splitting comedy, we find out why.  With hilarious new routines from a menagerie of puppet freaks and "wanna-be" replacements, this dark and edgy show will leave you in stitches.
title: Strassman Live Vol. 4: Ted E's Farewell
